            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# MacHelper Pro 1.0.0

## What's New

- Improves app startup performance by avoiding launch-time icon pixel scanning.
- Keeps Check for Updates responsive by moving Finder permission probing out of the synchronous menu refresh path.
- Improves Finder right-click menu configuration, icons, and permission state handling.
- Improves Auto Wi-Fi Switch permission handling and startup behavior.

Requires macOS 13.0 or later.
]]></description>
